            {
              "block_type": "paragraph-1",
              "text": "The process for the drawdown and liquidation of property of UNITAD was guided by the principles of and policies contained in Financial Rule 105.23. The assets of UNITAD, with a total capitalized value/acquisition value of $12,304,751 (corresponding net book value/operational value of $5,350,308), were disposed of as at 31 December 2024, of which 96.7 per cent have been transferred to UNAMI, UNSOS and UNMISS, while the rest were written off or sold locally.",
              "table_content": null,
              "hyperlinks": [],
              "children": []
            },
            {
              "block_type": "paragraph-1",
              "text": "A summary of the final disposition of all assets is reflected in table 69 below.",
